{"id": 5768, "title": "Ticket #5768: DC daemons should automatically get -localname flag if appropriate.", "description": "<blockquote>\nIf the master knows that DAEMON_NAME is a DC daemon, and if DAEMON_NAME is not in the hard-coded list of known daemons, then the master should start that daemon with the <code>-localname</code> flag set to DAEMON_NAME.\n\n<p>This will make &lt;DAEMON_NAME&gt;.&lt;parameter&gt; much more useful, and should substantially reduce the need to set &lt;DAEMON_NAME&gt;_ARGS.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2016-Aug-23 11:12:12 by johnkn:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>CODE_REVIEW</strong> -local-name argument should only be added if the user doesn't supply one in config.\n\n<p></p><hr/>\n<em>2016-Aug-24 09:32:25 by johnkn:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>CODE_REVIEW</strong> looks good</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5849\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5849'); return false;\" title='Resolve log configuration madness for \"clone\" daemons.'>#5849</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nResolve log configuration madness for \"clone\" daemons.</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5852\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5852'); return false;\" title=\"Eliminate need to set &lt;SUBSYS&gt;_ARGS.\">#5852</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nEliminate need to set &lt;SUBSYS&gt;_ARGS.</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"abandoned\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5958\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5958'); return false;\" title=\"DC daemon flag '-local-name' should be changed to '--localname'\">#5958</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nDC daemon flag '-local-name' should be changed to '--localname'</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"abandoned\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6039\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6039'); return false;\" title=\"Daemon client should ignore LOCALNAME param prefix when self==subsys\">#6039</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nDaemon client should ignore LOCALNAME param prefix when self==subsys</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Nov-29 11:02</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/1c80daa5fc9e5a08237db6d8d15f2034653cea6f\">[49672]</a></span>: fix previous commit for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5768\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5768'); return false;\" title=\"DC daemons should automatically get -localname flag if appropriate.\">#5768</a></span> for Clang builds  (By John (TJ) Knoeller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Nov-28 16:50</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nC